A massive golden serpent coiled around a glowing fiber optic cable network suspended in space, its scales made of dollar bills and corporate logos, squeezing the luminous data streams flowing through the cables while smaller fish-like creatures representing websites desperately swim through the narrowing gaps, the serpent's eyes gleaming with hunger, set against a dark cosmic backdrop with dying stars, rendered in cyberpunk style with neon accents of electric blue and toxic green, sharp angular shadows, chrome reflections, and a gritty dystopian atmosphere suggesting corporate domination over digital freedom.
